config/cluster/v3/circuit_breaker.proto`): The `CircuitBreakers.Thresholds` message defines `max_connections` (field 2, default 1024) and `max_pending_requests` (field 3, default 1024) as `google.protobuf.UInt32Value` fields that control when the overflow condition is triggered."
